welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Waggaman, a charming city known for its beautiful parks and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay and make unforgettable memories!"

airports.airport_name: Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport houses all airline check-in counters, baggage claim, security checkpoints, and a variety of dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport serves domestic and international flights, with gates A1-A7.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport serves domestic flights, with gates B1-B9.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. No password is required.
